title: Lock
description: Keyhole in center of long side.  Above the keyhole, on a cushion, a rod with the Hand of Justice, and a rod with the fleur-de-Lis, crossed through a Crown of Thorns.  Winged heads of cherubin to right and left of keyhole, terminating in foliage scrolls.
name: Lock
